     <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">James Kochan</ENAMEX> , chief fixed-income <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">strategist</ENAMEX> at <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION:CORPORATION">Merrill Lynch</ENAMEX> , is touting shorter-term securities , which he says should benefit more quickly than longer-term bonds as interest rates fall .
