     After <TIMEX TYPE="DATE:DURATION">several years</TIMEX> of booming business with <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE:COUNTRY">China</ENAMEX> , foreign <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">traders</ENAMEX> are bracing for the biggest slump in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE:DURATION">a decade</TIMEX> .
